'''聖保羅禮拜堂'''（St. Paul's Chapel）是位於[[紐約市|紐約市]][[下曼哈頓|下曼哈頓]][[百老匯|百老匯]]209號的一座[[美國聖公會|美國聖公會]]教堂，也是曼哈頓現存最古老的教堂建築<ref>{{cite inside}}, p. 108</ref>。聖保羅禮拜堂竣工於1766年，是當時紐約最高的建築。1960年，聖保羅禮拜堂被列入[[美國國家歷史名勝|美國國家歷史名勝]]<ref name="nhlsum"/><ref name="nrhpinv">{{cite web |url=http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/66000551.pdf |date=October 11, 1975 |first=Patricia |last=Heintzelman |title=National Register of Historic Places Inventory-Nomination: St. Paul's Chapel |format=pdf |website=National Park Service |access-date=2016-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524181444/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Text/66000551.pdf |archive-date=2011-05-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="nrhpphotos">{{cite web |url=http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/66000551.pdf |title=National Register of Historic Places Inventory-Nomination: St. Paul's Chapel—Accompanying photos |format=pdf |date=1975 |website=National Park Service |access-date=2016-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406095605/http://pdfhost.focus.nps.gov/docs/NHLS/Photos/66000551.pdf |archive-date=2012-04-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
